sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Router<br/>Platform-managed
    participant vLLM as vllm-rocm Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as AMD ROCm GPU<br/>PCIe/ROCm
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over vLLM,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup

    vLLM->>Storage: Load model weights<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or HTTPS/443 (S3)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount / IAM
    Storage-->>vLLM: Model artifacts
    vLLM->>GPU: Load model into GPU memory<br/>PCIe/ROCm

    opt If model not pre-cached
        vLLM->>HF: Download model/tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        HF-->>vLLM: Model files
    end

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible HTTP Inference

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/completions<br/>or /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    KServe->>vLLM: HTTP/8000<br/>No pod-level encryption<br/>No pod-level auth
    vLLM->>GPU: Inference computation<br/>PCIe/ROCm
    GPU-->>vLLM: Inference result
    vLLM-->>KServe: JSON response<br/>HTTP/8000
    KServe-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference

    Client->>KServe: gRPC GenerationService<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    KServe->>vLLM: gRPC/8033<br/>No pod-level encryption<br/>No pod-level auth
    vLLM->>GPU: Inference computation<br/>PCIe/ROCm
    GPU-->>vLLM: Inference result
    vLLM-->>KServe: gRPC response/8033
    KServe-->>Client: gRPC response
